To fix the "Random Select" button, I will update `components/CharacterSelect.tsx`.

The previous issue was that the randomization logic relied on a `<canvas>` element (for a wheel animation) that was missing from the render output, causing the code to hang indefinitely in the "SPINNING" state. I will replace the canvas dependency with a robust overlay animation system that shows the random selection process and automatically confirms the selection after a short delay.

